cocaine-framework-native (0.11.1.5) unstable; urgency=low

  * Hide all internal symbols except type info and exceptions.
    This is the default behavior for clang with modern linkers, but our ancient
    GCC stupidly exports all mean-to-be-hidden symbols no matter what.

